section:
&reftitle.install;
To install the AMQP PHP extension, you must first install the librabbitmq library. Use the following steps to download and install the library:
# Download the rabbitmq-c library hg clone http://hg.rabbitmq.com/rabbitmq-c cd rabbitmq-c # Add the codegen requirement hg clone http://hg.rabbitmq.com/rabbitmq-codegen codegen # Configure, compile and install autoreconf -i && ./configure && make && sudo make install
&pecl.info;
Note to Windows users: This extension does not currently support Windows since the librabbitmq library does not yet support Windows.
